# HERMES.local.md — Project Rules (SBTDD)

> This file contains project-specific rules at the local level. Agents **read
> and enforce** these rules; they never modify them (see §2.4).
>
> The following files and directories are **gitignored** and are never tracked:
> `HERMES.md`, `HERMES.local.md`, `.hermes/` (entire directory), `sbtdd/`, and
> `planning/`. Add all of them to the project `.gitignore`.

